## Objective
The objective of this room was to understand basic networking concepts, how devices communicate over a network, and the fundamental components involved in data transmission.

## Environment
- Platform: TryHackMe
- Operating System: N/A
- Access Method: Web-based learning room

## Concepts Covered
- What a network is
- IP addresses (IPv4 basics)
- MAC addresses
- Ports and protocols
- TCP vs UDP
- Client-server model
- How data is sent across networks
